org.apache.flex.swf.tags

Class CSMTextSettingsTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.swf.tags.Tag
      • org.apache.flex.swf.tags.CSMTextSettingsTag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICharacterReferrer, ITag

    public class CSMTextSettingsTag
extends Tag
implements ICharacterReferrer
    Represents a CSMTextSettings tag in a SWF file.

    The CSMTextSettings tag modifies a previously streamed DefineText, DefineText2, or DefineEditText tag. The CSMTextSettings tag turns advanced anti-aliasing on or off for a text field, and can also be used to define quality and options.
